        " اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"لاَ تَدَعُوا اَلتِّجَارَةَ فَتَهُونُوا اِتَّجِرُوا بَارَكَ اَللَّهُ لَكُمْ\""
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3724 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"Do not abandon trade, lest you become insignificant. Engage in trade-may Allah (swt) bless you.\""
        ]
